[Episode 40]

23
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:22,240
Beasts in the human realm
wish to return home.

24
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:23,960
I fear that if it takes too long,

25
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,440
there will be more conflicts.

26
00:02:26,390 --> 00:02:27,750
Now Bai Ze is stirring again.

27
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:31,030
If we open the Portal

28
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,080
to let the beasts return home,

29
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:32,550
would it be better?

30
00:02:32,550 --> 00:02:33,270
Absolutely not.

31
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,670
If the Portal is opened,

32
00:02:36,110 --> 00:02:37,240
the Black Qilin King will emerge,

33
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,470
causing chaos in the world.

34
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:40,360
It will be even more terrifying
than Bai Ze.

35
00:02:42,630 --> 00:02:44,240
But now the Lotus Tower is crumbling,

36
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,160
the Black Qilin King will still emerge.

37
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:49,240
Or we can

38
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,750
simply defeat the Black Qilin King?

39
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:52,960
No one can defeat him.

40
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:55,600
The Black Qilin King's power
is too immense.

41
00:02:56,630 --> 00:02:57,630
Even back then, I

42
00:02:58,110 --> 00:03:00,390
along with Lotus and Lord Wuchang

43
00:03:00,750 --> 00:03:02,080
could not defeat him,

44
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,240
let alone now that he has Bai Ze.

45
00:03:10,670 --> 00:03:11,390
We'll think about

46
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,190
these matters in the future.

47
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:18,750
You don't look well.

48
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,000
You should rest early.

49
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:21,630
Don't worry.

50
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,240
You should rest early, too.

51
00:03:38,190 --> 00:03:38,720
Could it be

52
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,190
that I must become

53
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:41,630
the summoner of the Black Qilin King

54
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:43,240
and aid him to do evil?

55
00:04:23,070 --> 00:04:24,760
Black Qilin King!

56
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:04,640
What does this mean?

57
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,670
Could it be that the Black Qilin King
will reappear in the world?

58
00:05:23,070 --> 00:05:23,640
Bai Ze,

59
00:05:24,390 --> 00:05:26,600
since you claim that I am
the summoner of the Black Qilin King,

60
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:28,790
there's no way

61
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,600
to undo my seal in this world.

62
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:36,720
But now I already have a physical form,

63
00:05:41,950 --> 00:05:43,160
could I

64
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:45,200
end myself?

65
00:05:50,790 --> 00:05:51,350
Bai Ze.

66
00:05:52,550 --> 00:05:54,350
Even if I destroy myself,

67
00:05:55,670 --> 00:05:57,480
I will never allow disaster to occur.

68
00:06:02,390 --> 00:06:02,920
Chengbi.

69
00:06:06,110 --> 00:06:06,640
Qing.

70
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,160
Don't overthink it.

71
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,640
I have already come to terms
with Xiaoli's matter.

72
00:06:30,230 --> 00:06:31,040
Let's go down.

73
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:33,950
Alright.

74
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:03,670
What's wrong?

75
00:07:07,550 --> 00:07:08,640
I just feel that

76
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:12,440
we are very happy now.

77
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:20,350
We will remain happy forever.

78
00:07:44,790 --> 00:07:45,550
Let's go down.

79
00:07:51,110 --> 00:07:51,510
Come.

80
00:07:54,350 --> 00:07:55,040
Miss Zhu.

81
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:58,600
Miss Zhu,

82
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,070
how are you?

83
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:01,040
I'm fine.

84
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:02,000
Miss Zhu.

85
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,670
Sir,

86
00:08:04,950 --> 00:08:06,270
Tianxiang Restaurant is closed today.

87
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:08,830
This is my old friend, Lord Wuchang.

88
00:08:09,830 --> 00:08:10,480
Lord Wuchang,

89
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,950
why have you come at this time?

90
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:13,480
How is Fengyi?

91
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:16,160
Thank you for your concern,

92
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,270
she's doing fine.

93
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:20,200
But I sensed from the Water Palace

94
00:08:20,550 --> 00:08:21,950
that the Lotus Tower
has shown signs of disturbance.

95
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:24,000
This disturbance is intense

96
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,920
and extraordinary.

97
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,670
I couldn't rest assured,

98
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,160
so I came to take a look.

99
00:08:30,510 --> 00:08:31,230
Lord Wuchang,

100
00:08:31,670 --> 00:08:32,840
I have something to discuss with you.

101
00:08:33,350 --> 00:08:34,080
Come with me.

102
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:35,840
Alright.

103
00:08:36,030 --> 00:08:36,590
Qing,

104
00:08:37,590 --> 00:08:39,400
I'll chat with Wuchang.

105
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,150
Wait here for me.

106
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:02,350
You've already merged
with the Dragon's blood?

107
00:09:08,550 --> 00:09:09,840
I'm sure you know

108
00:09:11,710 --> 00:09:13,640
my blood is no different
from the Black Qilin King's.

109
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:15,840
It's even more evil and brutal than his.

110
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:18,230
It's just that day hasn't arrived yet.

111
00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:19,520
In those days, Master

112
00:09:21,110 --> 00:09:23,400
always spoke of
the impermanence of the world.

113
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,590
Who would've thought that today,

114
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,590
those words would come true?

115
00:09:28,590 --> 00:09:29,350
Lord Wuchang,

116
00:09:32,150 --> 00:09:33,280
I want to ask you for help.

117
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:35,440
When that day comes,

118
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,440
please end me,

119
00:09:45,230 --> 00:09:45,790
a Taotie

120
00:09:48,790 --> 00:09:51,200
that should've long disappeared
from this world.

121
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:42,400
Why have you summoned me?

122
00:10:45,150 --> 00:10:46,230
My good helper,

123
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:49,280
why are you angry already?

124
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:52,150
If I tell you a secret in a moment,

125
00:10:52,350 --> 00:10:54,230
you might be so angry
that you'd want to kill me.

126
00:10:54,670 --> 00:10:56,000
With a creature like you,
devoid of feelings

127
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:57,910
and driven by ambition alone,

128
00:10:57,910 --> 00:10:59,200
I truly have nothing to say.

129
00:10:59,550 --> 00:11:01,150
You have nothing to say to me

130
00:11:01,350 --> 00:11:03,670
but endless things to say to Taotie.

131
00:11:04,550 --> 00:11:05,670
But that's alright.

132
00:11:07,590 --> 00:11:09,110
She'll soon be dead.

133
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:10,760
What do you mean by that?

134
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:14,230
You two really are in sync,

135
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:17,030
even asking the same question.

136
00:11:17,350 --> 00:11:19,640
It seems Taotie
is deeply attached to you

137
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:21,400
and hasn't told you yet

138
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:23,400
that I've long known

139
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:25,440
you couldn't help me
obtain the Dragon's blood.

140
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,880
Because you succumbed to a human flaw.

141
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:29,760
You're blinded by emotions.

142
00:11:30,350 --> 00:11:31,080
But that's fine.

143
00:11:31,400 --> 00:11:33,000
At least you helped me
turn Zhu Chengbi

144
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,960
into a killing weapon for me.

145
00:11:35,470 --> 00:11:36,520
Did you think

146
00:11:36,520 --> 00:11:38,150
I didn't know you pretended
to approach me

147
00:11:38,150 --> 00:11:39,550
to help Taotie

148
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:41,200
break the Five Venoms Seal?

149
00:11:41,590 --> 00:11:42,840
But you certainly don't know

150
00:11:43,350 --> 00:11:44,590
I intentionally told you the secret

151
00:11:44,760 --> 00:11:46,320
of the Form-Revealing Herb.

152
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,280
Because only this way

153
00:11:47,280 --> 00:11:50,960
can Taotie and the Dragon's blood
merge into one.

154
00:11:52,590 --> 00:11:54,790
By the time the Lotus Tower
collapses tomorrow,

155
00:11:56,230 --> 00:11:59,520
Taotie will resonate
with the Black Qilin King,

156
00:11:59,590 --> 00:12:02,640
thus bringing the Black Qilin King
back to this world.

157
00:12:08,350 --> 00:12:10,000
There's one thing you also don't know.

158
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:12,710
Zhu Chengbi invited Wuchang back

159
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:15,150
just to have him help her kill herself.

160
00:12:43,750 --> 00:12:44,360
Lotus,

161
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:51,590
you should know what has happened.

162
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:01,270
Were you also

163
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:05,320
torn like this back then?

164
00:13:16,750 --> 00:13:17,590
Mr. Chang,

165
00:13:18,270 --> 00:13:19,150
all the affairs of the world

166
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:20,880
are predestined.

167
00:13:22,390 --> 00:13:23,680
Don't dwell on them too much.

168
00:13:32,070 --> 00:13:32,590
Wuchang,

169
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,240
I remember Lotus once said

170
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,680
you have the power to change
the heavens and the earth.

171
00:13:37,070 --> 00:13:38,070
With this string of prayer beads,

172
00:13:38,750 --> 00:13:40,240
you can alter the course of time.

173
00:13:43,630 --> 00:13:45,190
Could you make time flow backward

174
00:13:46,390 --> 00:13:48,480
to before I ever met Chengbi?

175
00:13:50,270 --> 00:13:50,880
Mr. Chang,

176
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,510
as far back as 500 years ago,

177
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:56,000
Master had already refused

178
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,680
to reverse time with me.

179
00:13:58,510 --> 00:13:59,680
That was his choice.

180
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:03,070
And now it's no longer that time,

181
00:14:03,070 --> 00:14:03,880
or that situation,

182
00:14:04,880 --> 00:14:06,440
so that choice is no longer available.

183
00:14:09,270 --> 00:14:09,710
Then

184
00:14:10,440 --> 00:14:11,710
is there any other way?

185
00:14:14,710 --> 00:14:16,000
The prayer beads are in your hands.

186
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:19,120
The answer is in your heart.

187
00:14:21,560 --> 00:14:25,000
Master left this treasure
to you back then.

188
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:28,000
There must be a reason behind it.

189
00:14:42,630 --> 00:14:44,270
Black Qilin King!

190
00:14:52,070 --> 00:14:53,360
So my recent dream

191
00:14:55,510 --> 00:14:57,360
of perishing together
with the Black Qilin King

192
00:14:58,510 --> 00:14:59,440
means this.

193
00:15:06,560 --> 00:15:07,680
You knew all along.

194
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:10,190
Why didn't you tell me back
in the Water Palace?

195
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:12,710
That string of prayer beads chose you.

196
00:15:13,680 --> 00:15:15,920
So I knew this outcome was inevitable.

197
00:15:17,040 --> 00:15:18,880
But at the time,
I couldn't bear to say it.

198
00:15:19,190 --> 00:15:21,590
I knew you and General
were deeply devoted to each other.

199
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:22,800
I thought

200
00:15:23,680 --> 00:15:25,480
perhaps there might be another way

201
00:15:25,950 --> 00:15:27,360
so you wouldn't have to part.

202
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:29,070
Thus at the time,

203
00:15:30,190 --> 00:15:32,270
I was unwilling to reveal this.

204
00:15:33,390 --> 00:15:36,480
But now the Lotus Tower is in turmoil,

205
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:38,150
Bai Ze is unleashing his beastly nature,

206
00:15:39,150 --> 00:15:41,480
Wuxia and even the human realm
are in grave danger.

207
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:43,190
I had no choice
but to come and tell you.

208
00:15:47,750 --> 00:15:49,070
As for what to choose,

209
00:15:53,150 --> 00:15:55,000
that is up to you, Mr. Chang.

210
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:59,440
Although Master
has delivered this quest,

211
00:15:59,950 --> 00:16:03,390
you still have the right
to decide for yourself.

212
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:28,630
It smells so good.

213
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:30,800
What delicious food
Miss Zhu's preparing?

214
00:17:31,560 --> 00:17:32,510
We don't know either.

215
00:17:33,150 --> 00:17:34,600
She won't let us in to help.

216
00:17:34,920 --> 00:17:36,110
We don't even know where Mr. Chang Qing

217
00:17:36,110 --> 00:17:37,270
and Lord Wuchang went.

218
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:38,600
Miss Zhu said

219
00:17:38,600 --> 00:17:40,150
she found inspiration for a new dish

220
00:17:40,150 --> 00:17:41,390
and won't let us in to help.

221
00:17:41,870 --> 00:17:42,680
Let's just stay here

222
00:17:42,680 --> 00:17:43,720
and wait patiently.

223
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:45,510
Alright then.

224
00:17:46,390 --> 00:17:47,960
But I'm so hungry now.

225
00:17:50,150 --> 00:17:51,320
So hungry.

226
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:13,560
This time,

227
00:19:15,320 --> 00:19:16,920
you don't have to pay the 300 liang.

228
00:19:20,350 --> 00:19:20,840
Chengbi,

229
00:19:23,680 --> 00:19:24,110
do you still remember

230
00:19:24,110 --> 00:19:25,680
what it was like when we first met?

231
00:19:26,110 --> 00:19:26,920
Of course, I remember.

232
00:19:28,080 --> 00:19:28,750
It was right here.

233
00:19:31,870 --> 00:19:33,560
The first time I saw you,

234
00:19:34,040 --> 00:19:34,750
I thought,

235
00:19:35,040 --> 00:19:36,350
where did this beggar come from?

236
00:19:36,680 --> 00:19:38,440
I didn't expect you could draw

237
00:19:38,870 --> 00:19:39,630
and do accounting.

238
00:19:40,750 --> 00:19:41,800
After cleaning up,

239
00:19:43,200 --> 00:19:43,990
you became quite good-looking.

240
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:06,920
Eat.

241
00:20:34,960 --> 00:20:38,320
If life could stay as when we first met.

242
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:52,680
I just remembered

243
00:20:53,720 --> 00:20:54,920
when I was young,
I could understand beast language,

244
00:20:56,040 --> 00:20:57,040
so I was quite different.

245
00:20:59,270 --> 00:21:00,390
The kids in the neighborhood

246
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:02,800
all bullied me

247
00:21:04,990 --> 00:21:08,200
and my father saw me as a disgrace.

248
00:21:11,040 --> 00:21:12,390
Only the demon beasts

249
00:21:13,800 --> 00:21:14,920
believed in me.

250
00:21:16,110 --> 00:21:17,560
I felt completely at ease with them.

251
00:21:19,320 --> 00:21:20,560
So I promised

252
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:23,150
to help them open the Portal

253
00:21:24,270 --> 00:21:25,320
and send them home.

254
00:21:27,320 --> 00:21:28,560
After coming to Tianxiang Restaurant,

255
00:21:32,040 --> 00:21:33,440
I've spent these years

256
00:21:34,230 --> 00:21:35,150
joyfully with you.

257
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:37,110
I fell in love with you.

258
00:21:40,350 --> 00:21:43,440
When I learned of my mission here,

259
00:21:44,800 --> 00:21:45,960
I have been hesitating

260
00:21:47,510 --> 00:21:48,630
about whether to open the Lotus Tower

261
00:21:50,510 --> 00:21:51,720
or to follow my heart

262
00:21:52,680 --> 00:21:54,200
and stay with you.

263
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:57,200
I don't know what to do.

264
00:22:00,800 --> 00:22:01,320
Chengbi,

265
00:22:03,800 --> 00:22:04,510
I'm sorry.

266
00:22:07,390 --> 00:22:08,990
I never intended to deceive you.

267
00:22:12,040 --> 00:22:12,870
I understand.

268
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:14,320
Qing,

269
00:22:16,040 --> 00:22:16,800
don't worry.

270
00:22:18,320 --> 00:22:19,750
You won't feel pain anymore.

271
00:22:22,560 --> 00:22:23,920
I could have repaid

272
00:22:25,560 --> 00:22:26,560
the 300 liang long ago.

273
00:22:28,870 --> 00:22:29,920
I didn't want to tell you

274
00:22:31,320 --> 00:22:33,040
because I wanted to stay by your side.

275
00:22:33,470 --> 00:22:34,150
I know.

276
00:22:52,720 --> 00:22:53,720
Look at those two.

277
00:22:54,470 --> 00:22:55,870
Are they going to have
a wedding banquet?

278
00:22:57,320 --> 00:22:58,870
What is a wedding banquet?

279
00:22:59,720 --> 00:23:00,470
In the human world,

280
00:23:00,560 --> 00:23:01,800
two people in love

281
00:23:01,800 --> 00:23:02,720
will become husband and wife.

282
00:23:03,040 --> 00:23:04,630
